TITLE: Configuring Multi-tenant Mode with JSON in Zero
DESCRIPTION: JSON structure for configuring per-tenant settings when running the Zero server in multi-tenant mode. This allows dispatching requests to different tenants based on host and path matching, with each tenant having its own environment variable overrides.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rocicorp/zero-docs/blob/main/contents/docs/zero-cache-config.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
